  int height)` [Game.h:103 / Game.cpp:1059] â€” one frame's work per call (`Os::update`, scheduler 
alter,
  `DirectInput::update`, network, `Clock::limitFrameRate`, `++ms_loops`). **`__cdecl`, EXACT 
parameter-list
  match to your `hkMainLoop` `__cdecl(bool presentToWindow, HWND, int width, int height)`.**

**Action:** re-pointed `game::mainLoop` from `&Game::run` â†’ `&Game::runGameLoopOnce`. **Name 
unchanged**, so
your existing `s_bindings[]` entry for `game::mainLoop` now resolves to the correct per-frame 
function with
