.\docs\research\swgclient-build.md:457:| 9 | **`.tre` asset archives** | `ClientMain.cpp` calls 
`SetupSharedFile::install(true, skuBits)` and immediately tries to open `misc/override.cfg` via 
`TreeFile::open`. With no `.tre` files reachable on the search path, you crash in setup before the 
window even appears. Not in the repo. |
.\docs\research\swgclient-build.md:458:| 10 | **A working `data/` tree on the search path** | Beyond 
`.tre`, the engine wants `data/sku.0/...` paths. Same gap as for the server — sourced from a retail 
install or `SWG-Source/client-assets`. |
.\docs\research\swgclient-build.md:488:4. At runtime: missing `.tre` asset archives, dead SOE auth, 
