codex
There is one small oddity in `GroundScene::load`: it computes `isSpace` but does not guard asteroid 
setup with it, so asteroid field setup is called for any scene using the derived scene id. That 
still supports the larger point: missing asteroid data should result in no fields, not a fatal, 
because the manager loads scene data through the shared asteroid generation layer and iterates what 
it gets.
